name: Experiment Or Die #101
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. It kinda feels like the flood gates have opened up and everyone is getting covid, but either the vaccines are working or Omicron isn't that big of a deal. Now as we look more and more for friendship and camaraderie in the real world we are fighting over tests so we can continue to travel and do all the social things we want to do. As much as we yearn for connection we still need to be patient and mindful and do what's best to keep our loved ones safe, at home, by the fire.
